        "content": "<p>First, I follow the suggestion writing induction and after finish the active goal, I write cases to depart the\"or\" option,,here is my code</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">induction</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">with</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">d</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hd</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">right</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">zero_le</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">cases</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hd</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">with</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hy</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">left</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">succ_eq_add_one</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">cases</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">with</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ha</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">ha</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">add_right_comm</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"n\">a</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üê</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">add_assoc</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rfl</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">left</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
